The paper discusses the process of populating a knowledge base using probabilistic inference and learning, which is a common topic in the field of database systems (cs.DB). The use of inference and learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions information extraction and integration, which are common topics in natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The focus on feature engineering, which is the process of selecting and constructing relevant features for a machine learning model, suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG).
